snippet.title: SmarterEveryDay
snippet.description:
I explore the world using science.  That's pretty much all there is to it.  Watch 2 videos. If you learn something AWESOME, please subscribe if you feel like I earned it.

Contact: http://www.smartereveryday.com/contact.  I currently get lots of correspondence so please forgive me if I'm unable to reply.  I mean well, but want to focus on being a better Dad.
